    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款第三人称与第一人称结合的游戏中指挥二战时期的坦克排。参与真实而战术性的战斗，重现历史战场。体验完整的战役模式，或在遭遇战模式中测试你的战术能力，扮演德军或美军作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/262bc86810563c6cf9269923d4d0f2b1.poster.avif?t=1766086757\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/262bc86810563c6cf9269923d4d0f2b1.webm?t=1766086757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/262bc86810563c6cf9269923d4d0f2b1.mp4?t=1766086757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为1944年的德国指挥官，你的任务是抵御在法国推进的敌军。组建你的坦克排，亲自指挥并带领他们在一系列激烈而战术的战斗中奋战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/01009ceb0f91cb3424203397bd31266a.poster.avif?t=1766086757\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/01009ceb0f91cb3424203397bd31266a.webm?t=1766086757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/01009ceb0f91cb3424203397bd31266a.mp4?t=1766086757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你的部队将在二战关键时刻扮演重要角色。重温圣洛、莫尔坦以及阿登地区的标志性战役，参与史上最伟大的坦克大战之一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/c8d057a7d2c8794a371e3efb5ef0af9b.poster.avif?t=1766086757\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/c8d057a7d2c8794a371e3efb5ef0af9b.webm?t=1766086757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/c8d057a7d2c8794a371e3efb5ef0af9b.mp4?t=1766086757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遭遇战模式——这一深受玩家喜爱的特色（源自我们的前作《Call to Arms: Gates of Hell》）强势回归，并带来更多扩展玩法。你可以选择历史冲突中的任一阵营作战，指挥强大的武器，例如标志性的虎式坦克或StuH 42。为争夺关键战略要地而战，带领部队走向胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/f31ee73d5f9c3b9f757d5061cf3534dd.poster.avif?t=1766086757\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/f31ee73d5f9c3b9f757d5061cf3534dd.webm?t=1766086757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/f31ee73d5f9c3b9f757d5061cf3534dd.mp4?t=1766086757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中逐渐了解你的乘员。随着战役的推进，体验他们的个人故事、胜利与艰辛，并见证他们的成长与变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/f5b08386ad7e1d9c561f19a0c4aa1cf0.avif?t=1766086757\" width=616 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/c4466d5ab6276395f2a927166cee8e81.avif?t=1766086757\" width=616 height=262 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5个PvE战役任务：单人或合作模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9个PvPvE遭遇战任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全可破坏且沉浸式的环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20种可操控的战争载具：每个阵营各10种历史真实的坦克与装甲车辆</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于物理的弹道与复杂的伤害模拟</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343070/extras/584e188bf4b05d9f9387dbb47a39173a.avif?t=1766086757\" width=170 height=175 /></span></p>",
